flowchart TD
  U[User Browser / PWA] --> WEB[Next.js Web App]
  WEB --> DB[(PostgreSQL)]
  WEB --> AUTH[Auth.js]
  WEB --> API[API Routes]

  CRON[Scheduler / Cron] --> Q[Queue]
  Q --> WORKER[Worker]

  WORKER --> SA[Source Adapters]
  SA --> RSS[RSS Feeds]
  SA --> HN[Hacker News API]
  SA --> GDELT[GDELT]
  SA --> TRENDS[Trend APIs]
  SA --> STATUS[Status Pages]

  WORKER --> DB
  WORKER --> RANK[Ranking Engine]
  RANK --> SUM[LLM Summarizer]
  SUM --> VALIDATE[JSON Schema Validation]
  VALIDATE --> DB

  WORKER --> EMAIL[Email Provider]
  WORKER --> PUSH[Web Push / FCM]

  DB --> ADMIN[Admin Dashboard]
